text: Okaloosa County is a county in the U.S. state of Florida, and was formed on June 13, 1915. As of 2020, 211,668 people lived there. Okaloosa County's seat is Crestview. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official county website Category:Florida counties Category:1915 establishments in the United States Category:1910s establishments in Florida
